She was also identified with Demeter. The intercourse between the Greeks and Egyptians led to the, partial identification of their divinities and the im- porting of Egyptian worship into Greece, from whence, or from Greek colonies, they passed to Rome. ‘ Candida ' refers to the story of the white cow into which Io was changed.
